{"tid":60223,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲 你哋點睇呢類人","createTime":"2016-12-30T09:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T00:21:55.000Z","uid":17554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"399c56b558e02f1f42f1e7c35033a6cda3a99f5a","tid":60223,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:27:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n大學做group project啦，總共四個人，有兩個人唔係major所以唔熟課題都算啦，但另外一個groupmate（係major)平時讀書好叻既，但佢一開始就叫我(我都喺major)擔大旗做曬啲整合同報告頭尾咁。之後我整合曬所有嘢，我都有分階段每次post上group俾大家睇睇我既進度，佢都客客氣氣又話無問題又盛。點知到最後final version又突然屌鳩我地整咗份垃圾出嚟，又話我哋做埋曬啲唔知咩嘢出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗你唔早啲講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到最後關頭先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S. 佢讀書喺真喺超叻，但性格好差（平時表現扮曬謙咁，但背後會插到人一文不值）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea90fabe096985059b54fd443ab665199b15ecfb","tid":60223,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:32:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"538b8c14c82d2338822d80ce942bc8a77fa89ea2","tid":60223,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"febfcb84b4bf01d5ecbbbd943102c4fc4c7e3597","tid":60223,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:33:49.000Z","msg":"拎番佢曾經講過既客氣說話<br />\n<br />\n問佢依D乜野黎"},{"pid":"917b3660767ee70c9881407f10eec3488a164164","tid":60223,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:34:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大把呢類人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪由佢罵囉，又唔會少忽肉嘅<br />\n<br />\n咪睇佢出到社會點樣仆街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　（當然唔排除佢會好成功啦&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n總之你一介意你就輸了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又無話特別好介意既 不過佢早啲話俾人知好啲啦<br />\n<br />\n一開始如果佢想用佢自己果套 就好心佢自己擔番大旗啦<br />\n<br />\n又唔想負責 人地花咗好多時間做完 又俾人話垃圾"},{"pid":"23ba4802f81f13411d8f5b94cfbd23f942b641a8","tid":60223,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拎番佢曾經講過既客氣說話<br />\n<br />\n問佢依D乜野黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實成個framework喺我地一齊諗<br />\n<br />\n但佢好鍾意人地要跟佢自己果套<br />\n<br />\n又批評啲non-major 唔識 我心諗人哋唔識都正常 洗唔洗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e478e2c9909dd17e8470158a9eba3e853c326fe5","tid":60223,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:37:59.000Z","msg":"抽起佢個名 叫佢自己一組<br />\n咁都仲要忍？你會唔會弱左少少"},{"pid":"073ea8b79041e12f2be37aec46c8cc86e197c16a","tid":60223,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抽起佢個名 叫佢自己一組<br />\n咁都仲要忍？你會唔會弱左少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我哋細班 之後仲要同佢繼續上堂 我留一線姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88b3ef190751bec0c2fb62e67ec4e44dafec7df1","tid":60223,"uid":41859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>抽起佢個名 叫佢自己一組<br />\n咁都仲要忍？你會唔會弱左少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我哋細班 之後仲要同佢繼續上堂 我留一線姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br /